## Memory & Knowledge

This workspace uses a layered memory system. Optionally, it integrates with **cognee** for semantic search across the corpus.

| Layer | Location | Populated by |
|-------|----------|--------------|
| Personal curated | `<workspace>/.claude/memory/{MEMORY,lessons-learned}.md` | `/bye` |
| Per-project knowledge | `<workspace>/projects/<slug>/.claude/memory/` | `/bye`, committed for repos |
| Identity | `<workspace>/me/{identity,brag-log,growth,team}.md` | `/setup-workspace`, `/bye` |

